+- **Scope**: 4 diagnostic scenarios — unreachable, auth failure, timeout, 404
+- **Acceptance criteria**: Valid YAML frontmatter, ≥3 scenarios with symptom→diagnosis→fix, dual reviewer PASS
+- **Constraints**: Read-only access to other agents, no Unison code modification, snapshot safety
